    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-800b-9ce0-d4e2cf384331",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Predicting performance and Dropout are important research questions to address. Authors employ multiple algorithms to identify students at-risk and predict dropout. The model predicts end-of-program success  and follows a standard ML pipeline using 10-fold Cross-validation. Best models, evaluated using AUC score, were GBoost (0.808) and Deep Learning (0.811).",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-800b-9ce0-d4e2cf384331",
